\intbl \ql \b Background\b0 \line Cornerstone Performance Solutions is a new institution which is not yet registered with the Department of Higher Education and Training and is not yet accredited to offer higher education programmes by the HEQC. According to the institution it has been offering programmes accredited by BANKSETA in the Financial Services Sector. a Simiar programme\'2C a National Certificate in Banking\'2C was applied for in 2010\'2F11 and not accredited. \line \line In 2009 the institution applied for the National Certificate in Banking Level 5 \'2861589\'29 and the programme was not accredited.\line \cell \pard 

\intbl \row \pard 
\line \par\pard\trowd\trqc \trpaddl113\trpaddt113\trpaddb113\trpaddr113\trpaddfl3\trpaddft3\trpaddfb3\trpaddfr3\trgaph100\trrh100\trleft36
